# License Grants Policy

**Substantial Contributions** (eligible for listing in LICENSORS):
- New lore (factions, cities, realms)
- New systems or mechanical frameworks
- Major expansions to setting cosmology or SRD structure

**Minor Contributions** (not eligible):
- Typos, formatting, minor rewrites
- Clarifications without material new content

Substantial contributors will be publicly listed in LICENSORS upon PR merge approval.
